@node "DISTRIBUTION" "Distribution"

I, Pavel Fedin, allow to distribute and modify this software freely. I'm not
the original author, so i leave the original conditions unchanged.

Anyone may do anything to this archive within the following constaints:

This document file must be included with all distributions of any part of
this archive (except with the 3 libraries listed above).

Full credit to the original author of WBStartup+ and WBStartup+Prefs
(John Hughes) must be given in any modified source code, or executable
which is redistributed from this archive.  People who modify the source code
may also include there names for possible future 2nd party updates.

@endnode

@node "FUTURE" "Future"

  In future it is possible to extend WBStartup+Prefs to control WBStartup++'s
  options. I can do it if somebody will wish it.
  Unfortunately i don't have much time, and it's not my only project (and is
  not primary one), so i don't know when i'll implement this. If you wish to
  help, you are welcome!

@endnode


@node "INSTALL" "Installation Instructions"


  @{b}INSTALLATION:@{ub}


  The installation is easy. Just copy the "WBStartup+Prefs" executable
  anywhere you want (usual place for it is "SYS:Prefs" drawer.
@endnode

