@node "SYNOPSIS" "Features"

   @{b}Features@{ub}

  WBStartup+Prefs is designed to be an alternative preferences editor for the
  "WBStartup++" program by Frank Fenn <fenn@nucleus.com>, but also will work
  with old "WBStartup+" program. Actually this project is part of WBStartup+.
  When i had installed AmigaOS v3.5 i discovered that my old good WBStartup+
  program doesn't show icons. Also there was some other little problems. So
  i decided to take care of this program and rework it for OS v3.5. But when
  i started this work i discovered that there was already a project called
  WBStartup++, which worked under OS v3.5. So my project became senseless, but
  i didn't want to abandon it because i've had already spend some time on it.
  So i decided to partially finish the work and here's the result. I should
  say, i like my preference editor more than WBStartup++'s native. Now you've
  got a choice too.
  @{b}
@ENDNODE

